{"tid":1534610,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我正式宣布所有非前線香港人都有潔癖，自私自利","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T08:26:09.000Z","uid":81236,"like":86,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"5f11e89b9c82a965644bb9973a84b784db8e7ede","tid":1534610,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:13:29.000Z","msg":"口說杯葛，但餐廳照食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口說恐襲，但生活如常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n口說光復，但見狗就跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n口說革命，但又怕流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只可以話抱住必死心態既義士行得太前，香港人真係欠左你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民眾既就繼續自私自利<br />\n<br />\n而家連校園都入侵埋啦，已經污染埋大家既下一代<br />\n<br />\n以後大家既子女就會成為佢地眼中既曱甴，返學校見到佢地就要九十度鞠躬<br />\n<br />\n義士被私刑，譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n義士被爆眼，譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n女義士被非禮羞辱，譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民被黑社會無差別打，譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民被黑警地鐵無差別打，譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家既底線仲有幾多條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n其實大家同中國外交部有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n雖軟必豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"6e2dae21f8489f8e5065abe261d56dc7433b51b0","tid":1534610,"uid":123991,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:13:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c5a585516773558621dd7122634b81ba6522897","tid":1534610,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:13:56.000Z","msg":"香港人欠左前線義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8e477aac2544ace8e4dc580b1a4bdd6b9fbba1","tid":1534610,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:14:17.000Z","msg":"香港人欠左死諫既義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87b6304f79a146c04981ba931a9cd8d2f0a2066","tid":1534610,"uid":81236,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:14:51.000Z","msg":"香港人欠左被羞辱既女義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e373ce1b9047f61d364c8ab90552d62bf789ca","tid":1534610,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:15:19.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"54cef010f97672c7bec29b4de8a25dcdd1a28ca3","tid":1534610,"uid":38494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:15:33.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金 全民提款日</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"d6e1bbd465a8116196a7c0919b7a9764baee5ac9","tid":1534610,"uid":284264,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:15:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又分化<br />\n不推文回覆</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"dc8d516bdd1e99f39c4b312cd6b9d92bef414ed9","tid":1534610,"uid":108347,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:16:29.000Z","msg":"你激將法有尻用咩<br />\n<br />\n難聽啲講句，一千人被捕根本即係絕絕絕大部分香港人未上身，到身邊總有一個人比人拉比人打，先有得升級，而家黑警正正喺到幫我地招兵買馬<br />\n<br />\n冇人想多人比人拉，但係現實就係現實，對抗極權大部分人係淆低先，跟住要成功有兩步，見到希望，之後自己克服恐懼行前，而家大家行咗第一步，有希望，但係大部分人未上身，未主動行前<br />\n<br />\n革命都係迫出嚟，而家日日亂拉係好事，佢逾係亂咁拉就逾多人抱不平，到個個見到鄰居係講呀邊個邊個都比人拉咗而唔係咦你落街呀，到時就係全面反擊嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n其實甚至未必需要，而家已經有黑警啪藥神智不清咁開工，狗仔狗女好快一係自殺一係怪責自己狗老豆狗老母，冇錯拖係會好多人被捕犧牲，但係佢加埋武警都係幾萬人(大部分狗係文識)，我地3個月都係拉得1千，拖落去點都係我地贏，最後一係黑警頂唔順眾叛親離，一係拉到全民起義"},{"pid":"d28d0671815154d49b9964931c50c74c2628907d","tid":1534610,"uid":134134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:16:31.000Z","msg":"返工&gt;光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"6ae2b89ee8de3131f85668b16db1d3bf6b3e0607","tid":1534610,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f11e89b9c82a965644bb9973a84b784db8e7ede","tid":1534610,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:13:29.000Z","msg":"口說杯葛，但餐廳照食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口說恐襲，但生活如常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n口說光復，但見狗就跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n口說革命，但又怕流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只可以話抱住必死心態既義士行得太前，香港人真係欠左你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民眾既就繼續自私自利<br />\n<br />\n而家連校園都入侵埋啦，已經污染埋大家既下一代<br />\n<br />\n以後大家既子女就會成為佢地眼中既曱甴，返學校見到佢地就要九十度鞠躬<br />\n<br />\n義士被私刑，譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n義士被爆眼，譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n女義士被非禮羞辱，譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民被黑社會無差別打，譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民被黑警地鐵無差別打，譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家既底線仲有幾多條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n其實大家同中國外交部有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n雖軟必豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:17:09.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n有時候行商場見到連罷食都做唔到真心唔滿意"},{"pid":"9aecc765d81acd2d63e2a3b5e9cc994ff5f45bfd","tid":1534610,"uid":18628,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:19:11.000Z","msg":"我只可以講真係左膠禍港 發夢喺前線打生打死 左膠就full gear（仲靚裝過我）咁喺中後排叫你走 唔好打唔好打 屌你咩 未有心理準備就番歸咪撚阻住啦"},{"pid":"88cb78fbe3294fab752fe01a043aa741f8cdfb68","tid":1534610,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:19:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2e4c444607b78f7f75a1fdc89c1383b4f3d5ba9","tid":1534610,"uid":61115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:26.000Z","msg":"無撚計 大部份都係冷氣軍師"},{"pid":"6d6d4f8216808f5f1fdbe1a927cf927214466a6f","tid":1534610,"uid":81236,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6e1bbd465a8116196a7c0919b7a9764baee5ac9","tid":1534610,"uid":284264,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:15:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又分化<br />\n不推文回覆</span></span></strong