y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民眾既就繼續自私自利<br />\n<br />\n而家連校園都入侵埋啦，已經污染埋大家既下一代<br />\n<br />\n以後大家既子女就會成為佢地眼中既曱甴，返學校見到佢地就要九十度鞠躬<br />\n<br />\n義士被私刑，譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n義士被爆眼，譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n女義士被非禮羞辱，譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民被黑社會無差別打，譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民被黑警地鐵無差別打，譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家既底線仲有幾多條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n其實大家同中國外交部有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n雖軟必豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:34:01.000Z","msg":"冇分別，一樣係嘴砲only <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6070010cd24964736ad7533c65d1ac020e4657d","tid":1534610,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:34:04.000Z","msg":"添馬呢？ 人呢？"},{"pid":"21d02d43f7bb9743011bf46c5cff1f083f85f744","tid":1534610,"uid":240555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f11e89b9c82a965644bb9973a84b784db8e7ede","tid":1534610,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:13:29.000Z","msg":"口說杯葛，但餐廳照食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口說恐襲，但生活如常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n口說光復，但見狗就跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n口說革命，但又怕流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只可以話抱住必死心態既義士行得太前，香港人真係欠左你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民眾既就繼續自私自利<br />\n<br />\n而家連校園都入侵埋啦，已經污染埋大家既下一代<br />\n<br />\n以